Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:54.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Will Appear inn World Championships}

Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:36.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san! Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there, Inokuma Yawara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:43.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we get a comment? Hey, Yawara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, you fine gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:02:02.39,epTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.3\be1\pos(320,410)\3c&H3548D5&\c&H4137FD&}You're Going to the World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:05.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Jigoro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddaya mean "just"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:11.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see why all you reporters are flooding this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:14.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara won the All-Japan Selected Tournament yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and is going to the World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't think up a better article than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer any questions you want. Go ahead, ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we're here for something bigger than her victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the morning sports papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:37.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they're spilling a lot of ink about Yawara-san's job prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.29,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Headlines: Struggle! We Want Yawara-chan!\NThree Companies Make Claims on Hotly Pursued Yawara#
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:36.42,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,20)\fad(300,0)}Headlines: Ginza Can-Can, Oshiuri Travels, Mini House\N Yawara's Future Plans? Vicious Struggle for Inokuma Yawara!#
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:41.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Oshiuri Travels, Ginza Can-Can,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:47.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Mini House all claimed Yawara for themselves at yesterday's tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:51.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Newspapers add so much color these days that it hurts my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:57.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see {\i1}All Sports{\i0\fscx170} {\r\}is spreading unfounded rumors again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.40,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Headline: Inokuma Yawara Headed for Saikai!!\N Ito Fujiko Joining in Double Transfer!!#
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:02.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll always be a third-rate paper if they keep writing that kind of garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:05.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. My gut tells me I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You nitwit! Who the hell writes articles based on his gut or a bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So where is Yawara-san going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Mini House is her top choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty, I think it's time to open up my clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:28.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys want a back rub or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to dodge the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:35.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost forgot. Please try these Amazing Monaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, at least give us a hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good. Where'd you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? And you'll get some more if you just give us something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:52.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Yawara ain't gonna be some trifling office lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going straight to Saikai U to play judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:56.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All Sports{\i0\fscx130} {\r\}got us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine yourself as some office lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:06.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd just waste your hard-earned money on pointless entertainment and men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:09.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, the editor is going to flay me for this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, {\i1}All Sports News{\fscx30} {\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:13.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's off to MWJC!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Saikai U!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:21.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She can fool around all she likes in the little time she has left at junior college.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:24.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ain't you gonna listen to me talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It might make a good story!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:36.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius! So you really did scoop them, Matsuda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:37.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An unflappable reporter who follows his instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the very model of a journalist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.64,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's going to continue her judo at Saikai U?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:50.70,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really play out that way?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll sell twice as many copies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.15,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Ito#
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.11,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she cry so much last night that she's too tired to wake up?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.16,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have classes today either.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san? Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san? Fujiko-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Ito-san, she left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.15,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be thoroughly upset.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.84,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She practiced her heart out for that tournament.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:49.14,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to go to the World Championships in Yugoslavia so much.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:58.08,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I have my own problems to worry about.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, take a look at these!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:10.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one saying she's going to Saikai U is {\i1}All Sports News.{\i0\}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:17.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should have stayed and made a final play for her instead of withdrawing so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:22.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Oshiuri gets her, we'll be in real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, will you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:31.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she come to us when we don't have a judo team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma Yawara is going to Saikai University.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:39.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she'll be on top of the world as the greatest judoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President! Chief of General Affairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? And knock at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sincerely sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:52.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is h-huge! I-Ino... Inoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:59.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call from Inokuma Yawara! She's going to stop by here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.57,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Cordial Travel - Hawaii#
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is she coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wh-Why," you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:09.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she must be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:12.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We came gallivanting in to recruit her,\N even though we don't have a judo team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.29,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Travel Office Reception#
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. Anyway, we have to be courteous. And I mean courteous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.38,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Parlor#
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:34.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish to apologize for what we did yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:36.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We congratulate you on your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:45.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.90,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:57.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You came all the way to the arena yesterday, but I wasn't considerate to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:01.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, we were the ones who tried to recruit you, despite our lack of a judo team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know I was being very selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:10.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We selfishly thought about how our earnings would double if we hired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I wonder if it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yutenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:27.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya get a swarm of reporters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they give you some Amazing Monaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:36.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Board of Trustees officially approved Ito Fujiko-san's admission,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,along with Yawara-san's!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All they have to do is take a simple entrance exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You did a bang-up job, Yutenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:49.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still need another favor from you about Beanpole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate this little victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't I treat you to some hairy crab ramen at the Rai-Rai Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I know I've come too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wish to work for Tsurukame Travel—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, for your esteemed company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely not out of the question, Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We implore you to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still don't have a judo team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:33.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still want to work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what about your transfer to Saikai University?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:46.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of going to Saikai University.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:51.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But your grandfather was sure that you'd go to Saikai U.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will there be problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:00.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll straighten things out.\N I'll convince him otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.01,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san isn't picking up.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:24.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to turn Grandpa around somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Fujiko-san is completely depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, it's all judo's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Judo is definitely the right path for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanazono-kun... and Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:47.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I always fail at the most important moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:53.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I promised Inokuma-san repeatedly that I'd go with her to Yugoslavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But during the critical championship match...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:01.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I did, I was just as pathetic as I've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:07.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I continue playing judo at Saikai U with Inokuma-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:12.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just remain a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that I'll just be a burden to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That simply doesn't apply to you, Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma needs you, Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:31.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma continues with judo because you're there for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:37.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And doesn't she see you as not just her friend, but as a real judoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inokuma-san sees me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:45.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you keep beating yourself up like you're doing now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma will be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:51.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, Hanazono Kaoru, more than Inokuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:12:00.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I get it, Hanazono-san. So please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stupid to get depressed over something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:24.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky to have someone to support you, Fujiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:27.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I didn't need to worry after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:54.41,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Headline: Teleshikova Explodes with an Uranage!\NDominates European Championship Free-Weight Class#
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara! Get in here! Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara! Hey, Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara, you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you yelling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner will be ready in a minute, so be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll love what we're having tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know food's important, but look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your gazpacho's all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what's this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazpacho, gazpacho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:43.49,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Book: Spanish Cooking#
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:43.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cold soup based on tomato juice. You eat it like a salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Spanish cuisine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this called "gas blasto"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "gazpacho"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.28,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:01.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See, isn't it delicious? That's called "Cordon Bleu."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Condor Brr"? Aren't those just port cutlets?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't pork cutlets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so grumpy and insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you call it, it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:15.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So how come you're putting some effort into your cooking lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:20.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get you in a good mood by serving you delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. Doesn't it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.88,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:32.47,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to break it to him gently that I'm working for Tsurukame Travel.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, almost forgot! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad manners to bring a newspaper to the dinner table.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.44,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Headline: Teleshikova Explodes with an Uranage!#
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, doesn't that stir your blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to take on this world-class player Tele-something-or-other after a dog's age!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddaya mean, "It doesn't matter"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:03.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They officially qualified you to represent Japan in the World Championships today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna get into one of your hissyfits again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You lying, no-account girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:21.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a very public, very firm declaration yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! You can do it, Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we'd go to Yugoslavia together, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Declaration? That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:38.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... just because Fujiko-san wanted to go so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:42.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Fujiko-san isn't going, then there's no point in me going either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still go to Yugoslavia even if you ain't gonna play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to win the World Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and go to Saikai University with Beanpole, and that's final!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to decide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.64,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't fight with him!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.61,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, all this delicious food will go to waste!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:18.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Inokuma! Yawara's going to Saikai U, and that's final!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still have something to say, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:28.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I put on the answering machine for those annoying recruiters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, it's Munakata of Oshiuri Travel Agency, in Human Resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish to set up a meeting with Inokuma Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you? Those lousy horseflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:45.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, what if we get an important call?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll just call 'em back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.95,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurukame Travel might have left me a message.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ginza Can-Can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:03.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mini House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:07.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry to keep disturbing you, but this is Munakata of Oshiuri—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't no calls for you to worry about! Now get in here and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:18.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mikawaya Sake. Your order—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to Ginza Can-Can—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:25.19,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I didn't make it in time to Tsurukame Travel.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:30.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! This is Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completely recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm ready and primed for the Canadian Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:43.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd hear your voice before my matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't worry, I'll be sure to win, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:49.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. See you again at the World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Master Jigoro! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an international call from Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jody, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:04.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to talk to her because you turned on the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear what Jody just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna meet you at the World Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do some drawn-out international call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just meet her in Yugoslavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come on, time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:30.04,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great timing, Jody.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.84,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,All she needs is one more push before she heads off to the World Championships.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.84,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Inokuma Yawara Officially Qualifies for World Championships, 48 kg-and-under Class#
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:42.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going way too smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:46.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That transfer to Saikai U and the World Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:50.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought Yawara would just continue on with judo without a peep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I should go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a good talk with her in some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And just who are you seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:08.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I was thinking I'd do an interview with that pro wrestler, Maeda Naota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:14.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, we never get any time alone lately, Kosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pout like that! Just don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsuda, cable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:26.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-chan, keep your office romance private!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good God...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:37.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's that huge woman from the Seoul tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She won the free-weight class at the Canadian Championships,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:43.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's now going to the World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So she's fully healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:52.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's competing in the World Championships? Good for you, Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't anything to cry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:59.39,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday Teleshikova won the European Championships,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.50,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and today Jody's big news.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.13,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Now she has no choice but to go.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're staring at empty space again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:10.26,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to appear in the World Championships, Yawara-san?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, let's grab some lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.35,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Meeting Room#
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We must proceed as carefully as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Inokuma Yawara came to us herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:25.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there are still several hurdles we need to clear before we employ her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:27.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:32.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, despite all the celebratory fireworks Oshiuri and the other firms are firing off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurukame Travel is Inokuma Yawara's first choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:39.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sit back and reel her in, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:45.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard a rumor that Oshiuri is planning to take her on a world cruise,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,making her into a captive audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll send her on two world cruises, or even three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said all we had to do is sit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, you can relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:06.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to a training camp to prepare for the World Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Oshiuri nor Mini House can get to her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can't get to her either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, there is that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:23.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that grandfather of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, her grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:31.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, for Beanpole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For me? Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:41.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:48.32,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurukame isn't calling me.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:53.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yawara, quit spacing out and go do some Uchi Komi or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:10.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:14.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Coach Yutenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:22.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I've been chosen as a practice partner for the Yugoslavia World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:24.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get to play in any matches,\N but I can still go to Yugoslavia with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:32.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:36.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:41.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's get you another gold medal at the World Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:52.89,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: The Barcelona Olympics in {\c&H5C74FF&}348{\r} Days#
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:01.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, Fujiko-san says she can come to Yugoslavia with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:06.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you and Beanpole are gonna get me two gold medals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:09.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Fujiko-san says she's just a practice partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you two are still playing judo in Yugoslavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:14.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:16.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko's First Training Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:22.83,nextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,30)\bord0.7\b1\be1\fs30\fscy100\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HCBD9EA&\pos(447,310)}Fujiko's First\N Training Camp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:20.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be getting my Nutcracker if you don't watch!
